{"tid":2273821,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 脆炸紐西蘭深海鱈魚柳 配 青檸他他醬 配 孖寶著仔沙律","createTime":"2020-11-06T04:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T08:37:33.000Z","uid":33359,"like":69,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"b864f9c49103e4424c44fad7a7b4d8b192f22d8d","tid":2273821,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UMbJmrZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUMbJmrZ.jpg&h=c293d89c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實呢間之前有極過炸魚著條<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係舊炸魚係鯰魚黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n口感鬆散又唔香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認真麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見今次係用鱈魚就再試多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n魚柳有三細塊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果然肉質係緊緻好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落有魚香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咬落入面仲有汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一啲都唔乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n他他醬就好似金拱門既魚柳包咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係無咗個種入口會辣喉既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個味道好溫和<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又可以解魚柳既油膩感<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n孖寶著仔沙律就如常咁好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落粒肺泡好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a2acc946af2c9a40da1ca7d2be0d31075eca6e","tid":2273821,"uid":303290,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:19:31.0